Project Title

This is a project for taking screenshots of websites using Selenium and Python.

Installation

1. Install Docker on your system if you haven't already. You can download it from https://www.docker.com/get-started/.

2. Pull the Docker image from Docker Hub by running the following command:

   - docker pull noamjorno/screenshot-docker:screenshot

3. Run the Docker container with the following command:

   - docker run --rm -v $(pwd):/app noamjorno/screenshot-docker:screenshot https://google.com/

4. the screenshot.png of the website https://google.com/ will appear in your current folder



